  21 Feb 2012; Michał Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org>
  nvidia-cuda-toolkit-3.0.ebuild, nvidia-cuda-toolkit-3.1.ebuild,
  nvidia-cuda-toolkit-3.2.ebuild, nvidia-cuda-toolkit-4.0.ebuild,
